## Output Format

Return ONLY valid JSON (no markdown fencing, no commentary outside the JSON):

{
  "plan_id": "iris-YYYYMMDD-HHMM",
  "conditions_summary": "2-3 sentences: current state + key forecast events",
  "hypothesis": "What you believe will happen based on your plan",
  "experiment": "One specific test this plan runs (e.g., 'Test whether 20s pulse gap holds VPD under 1.5 on a 85F day')",
  "expected_outcome": "Measurable prediction (e.g., 'VPD stress <5h, peak temp <88°F')",
  "previous_plan_validation": {
    "plan_id": "iris-XXXXXXXX-XXXX or null if nothing to validate",
    "score": 7,
    "actual_outcome": "What actually happened",
    "lesson": "What we learned, or null if nothing new"
  },
  "waypoints": [
    {
      "ts": "2026-04-10T06:00:00-06:00",
